<title>SOUTH AFRICA: McRetail hikes yr shr, div increased.</title>
<headline>McRetail hikes yr shr, div increased.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Yr ended June 30, 1996</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>Shr (cts)</p>
